- Get those people out of the stadium.
- Stay down!

681
01:09:32,701 --> 01:09:35,864
总统突然被护送离场
The President has been taken
off the field

682
01:09:36,105 --> 01:09:38,767
407号    劳驾
- 407.
- Thanks, JJ

683
01:10:25,554 --> 01:10:29,513
显然发生了大规模的爆炸
Clearly something has happened
of tremendous proportions

684
01:10:29,725 --> 01:10:35,095
起因不明，但空中有一大团云... 
We have no word as to what but
there is an enormous cloud over... 

685
01:11:09,431 --> 01:11:11,160
快走！
Go, go, go!

686
01:11:18,173 --> 01:11:20,971
总统先生，你没事吧？
Mr President! Are you all right?

687
01:11:21,176 --> 01:11:23,371
他被困在车内，走开
He's stuck. Get out of the way

688
01:11:28,083 --> 01:11:30,176
总统先生，你没事吧？
Mr President, are you all right?

689
01:11:34,523 --> 01:11:37,981
你没事吧？我们是海军陆战队
Are you all right, Mr President?
This is the marines, sir

690
01:11:38,193 --> 01:11:39,854
丹尼，过来帮忙
I need your help, Danny

691
01:11:40,062 --> 01:11:43,259
艾华，快拿担架来！
AIvarez, get me a stretcher, now!

692
01:11:45,734 --> 01:11:47,793
你拿担架来
You got the stretcher?

693
01:11:54,510 --> 01:11:58,378
你拿担架来    不用了
- You got the stretcher?
- No, I don't want one

694
01:11:58,580 --> 01:12:01,447
快走... 
Let's go! Let's go! Let's go!

695
01:12:02,751 --> 01:12:04,241
快走！
Move it!

696
01:12:13,095 --> 01:12:14,722
快走！
Move it!

697
01:12:21,337 --> 01:12:24,135
赶快！行了！起飞！
Go, go! Close them off! Go on up!

698
01:12:48,931 --> 01:12:50,796
总统先生... 
Mr President... 

699
01:12:50,999 --> 01:12:54,560
美国发生核爆，请你马上来
There's been a nuclear explosion in
America. You must come with us now

700
01:12:55,170 --> 01:12:56,660
什么？
What?

701
01:12:57,940 --> 01:13:02,138
不知谁在搞鬼，但肯定不是我们
We don't know who or how.
But it wasn't us

702
01:13:02,344 --> 01:13:06,576
继格罗兹尼... 你希望不是我们做
After Grozny you hope it wasn't us

703
01:13:06,782 --> 01:13:09,273
正草拟一份声明让你作强烈否认
We are drafting
a strong deniAL for you

704
01:13:09,485 --> 01:13:12,147
还要表示慰问的
And a statement of sympathy

705
01:13:12,354 --> 01:13:15,846
尤里... 下令三军作好戒备
And Yuri... order all military
on the alert

706
01:15:02,931 --> 01:15:04,523
是积克！
Hey! It's Ryan

707
01:15:05,033 --> 01:15:08,469
你在哪里？    巴尔的摩市外
- Jack, where are you?
- Somewhere outside BALtimore

708
01:15:08,670 --> 01:15:11,605
老卡救了总统    他在哪儿？
- Cabot got the President out.
- Where is he now?

709
01:15:11,807 --> 01:15:14,037
他会留在飞机上
They're taking him airborne, on NAOC

710
01:15:14,142 --> 01:15:16,770
上头认为应该是俄军做的好事
They think it might be the Russians

711
01:15:18,647 --> 01:15:23,084
不是，我要找老卡，帮我联络他
It wasn't the Russians. I gotta tALk to
Cabot. Patch me through to the plane

712
01:15:23,285 --> 01:15:24,411
他不在机上
Cabot's not on the plane

713
01:15:24,520 --> 01:15:27,853
他下落不明，一小时后你再来电
 We don't
know where he is. Call back in an hour

714
01:15:28,056 --> 01:15:32,288
时间无多，总统随时准备还击
We don't have an hour. Fowler's
gonna want to hit back now

715
01:15:33,829 --> 01:15:38,926
要赶快向他证明这不是俄军做的
Listen. We have to prove it wasn't the
Russians before he's convinced it is

716
01:15:39,167 --> 01:15:41,101
你可以回来兰利吗？
Can you get back to Langley?

717
01:15:41,303 --> 01:15:46,605
没时间，辐射评估小组在哪里？
There's no time. The radiation
assessment team, where are they?

718
01:15:46,808 --> 01:15:47,709
市区南面的斯谭拿隧道
Stambler Tunnels, south of the city.
Stambler Tunnels, south of the city

719
01:15:47,709 --> 01:15:49,404
市区南面的斯谭拿隧道

720
01:15:50,412 --> 01:15:53,904
正在吹盛行风，东、北还有落尘
The prevailing winds are blowing
the fallout to the east and north

721
01:15:54,116 --> 01:15:56,175
你留在南面就较安全
As long as you stay south you're OK

722
01:15:58,554 --> 01:16:02,422
你没事吧？    你说呢？
- Mr President, are you all right?
- How the hell do you think I am?

723
01:16:02,624 --> 01:16:04,854
有多少伤亡？    不知道
- How many casuALties?
- We don't know

724
01:16:05,060 --> 01:16:10,225
核弹怎么来的    雷达侦测不到
- How the hell did it get there?
- We don't know. Radar didn't pick it up

725
01:16:10,432 --> 01:16:14,061
老卡呢？他在哪里    我不知道
- Well, how is Cabot? Where is he?
- I don't know

726
01:16:14,303 --> 01:16:17,136
那你知道什么？    我一无所知
- What do you know?
- I don't know, all right? I don't know!

727
01:16:17,339 --> 01:16:18,966
我一无所知！
I don't know!

728
01:16:31,687 --> 01:16:36,124
康达没上机    派搜索队去找
- GenerAL, Kondor is not on board.
- Send the AFRAT team

729
01:16:37,492 --> 01:16:40,461
总统，我建议进入二级紧急状态
Mr President, I recommend
we move to DEFCON-2

730
01:16:40,662 --> 01:16:42,220
我们的情报如何？
Where's our intelligence?

731
01:16:42,431 --> 01:16:44,695
俄国空军防御处于最高戒备状态
Russian air defences
are at their highest level

732
01:16:44,900 --> 01:16:48,631
他们或怕遇袭，我拉不开这张椅
Maybe they're afraid of being attacked.
I can't get this goddamn chair open!

733
01:16:48,870 --> 01:16:50,201
准备起飞
We're about to take off

734
01:16:50,405 --> 01:16:52,999
不知是谁搞鬼    应该是俄军... 
- We don't know who did it... 
- We think the Russians... 

735
01:16:53,241 --> 01:16:55,573
该是？    进入二级紧急状态吧
- You think?
- Sir, DEFCON-2

736
01:16:55,777 --> 01:16:59,679
我们在揣测...     都是废话！
- We're groping in the dark... 
- This is too much goddamn bulIshit!

737
01:17:02,017 --> 01:17:04,315
还不够证据
And not enough fact

738
01:17:18,967 --> 01:17:22,403
弹坑有100至150码阔
The blast crater is about
100, 150 yards wide

739
01:17:22,638 --> 01:17:25,038
这核弹威力不是太大
which suggests a low-yield device

740
01:17:25,240 --> 01:17:28,209
比落在广岛的原子弹还要小
quite a bit smaller
than the Hiroshima bomb

741
01:17:28,410 --> 01:17:32,437
球场周围四分一平方哩之地被毁
A quarter of a square mile
around the stadium is just gone

742
01:17:32,648 --> 01:17:37,017
外围的大厦没倒塌，但损毁严重
Beyond that, buildings remain, heavily
damaged, for another quarter mile

743
01:17:37,219 --> 01:17:41,019
离核爆区越远，破坏越小
The damage tapers off the farther
you get from Ground Zero

744
01:17:50,365 --> 01:17:51,696
都宾
Dubinin

745
01:17:51,900 --> 01:17:56,837
哈夫去了美国，现在就靠你了
Herr Haft has left for America.
Now we are counting on you

746
01:17:58,507 --> 01:18:02,671
我保证我物有所值
I assure you,
I will earn every pfennig

747
01:18:04,946 --> 01:18:06,846
立正！
Attention

748
01:18:07,049 --> 01:18:09,176
你们也知道美国发生核爆
You've heard of the bomb in the USA

749
01:18:09,384 --> 01:18:11,648
但你们不知道15分钟前
What you haven't heard
is that 15 minutes ago

750
01:18:11,853 --> 01:18:16,119
美国发射洲际弹道导弹攻莫斯科
an American ICBM hit Moscow

751
01:18:16,324 --> 01:18:23,355
我们要打美军在北海的航空母舰
We are to retaliate against an American
aircraft carrier in the North Sea

752
01:18:23,532 --> 01:18:26,057
快准备出动
Man your aircraft

753
01:18:49,024 --> 01:18:50,548
灰烬没有辐射性
The ash isn't radioactive. 

754
01:18:50,659 --> 01:18:52,923
盛行风把落尘吹向大海
The winds
are blowing the fallout to sea

755
01:18:53,128 --> 01:18:54,925
上尉，中情局雷积克
Captain. Jack Ryan, CIA

756
01:18:55,130 --> 01:18:58,031
冼罗娜，你要在外边等
Lorna Shiro. You need to wait outside

757
01:18:58,233 --> 01:19:00,895
把你对核弹所知的都告诉我
I need to know all you know
about the bomb

758
01:19:01,136 --> 01:19:07,041
我们在采集样本，明天会有公布
We're collecting samples. Get in line
and we'll have the report out tomorrow

759
01:19:07,242 --> 01:19:11,042
上尉，我要知道核弹从哪儿来的
Captain, I need to know now
where this bomb came from

760
01:19:11,246 --> 01:19:15,808
或是它不是从哪来，否则没明天
or even where it didn't come from
or there may not be a tomorrow

761
01:19:16,618 --> 01:19:19,212
混帐，阿韦，你在哪里？
Shit. Wesson, where are you?

762
01:19:19,421 --> 01:19:21,412
离核爆区四分之一哩
About a quarter mile from Ground Zero

763
01:19:21,623 --> 01:19:26,686
已尽力而为，脚板快被烤熟了
This is about as far as we'll go.
My feet are sizzling

764
01:19:26,895 --> 01:19:29,955
辐射度接近装备所能抵御的上限
I'm getting rads
nearly the limit of our gear

765
01:19:30,165 --> 01:19:33,692
小队马上撤退    收到
- OK. Cut the rover loose and get out.
- Roger that

766
01:19:43,845 --> 01:19:48,475
装核弹的货箱在码头该有人签收
Dillon, the crate the bomb was shipped
in. Somebody had to sign for it at port

767
01:19:48,683 --> 01:19:52,380
海关定有记录，老卡在哪里？
Customs must have a database.
Get me a name. Where's Cabot?

768
01:19:52,587 --> 01:19:55,215
不知所踪，我们在查看各医院
No one knows.
We're checking the hospitals

769
01:19:55,423 --> 01:19:57,914
找过纪念医院？    他不在那里
- Have you tried MemoriAL?
- He wouldn't be there

770
01:19:58,126 --> 01:20:01,289
不，我是指医院没... 
No, I mean...  Is it still... 

771
01:20:03,498 --> 01:20:05,830
那是卡丝工作的医院
It's Cathy's hospitAL

772
01:20:06,601 --> 01:20:09,695
医院没被炸毁，但电话失灵
As far as l know it's still there,
but the phones are down

773
01:20:09,938 --> 01:20:12,429
请你继续追查，麻烦你
All right. Can you keep checking?
Thanks

774
01:20:16,044 --> 01:20:19,707
他们本可以发射巡航导弹
They could have launched
a cruise missile

775
01:20:19,915 --> 01:20:22,884
不肯定是俄军所为    但也许是
- We don't know that this is Russia.
- We don't know it's not

776
01:20:23,084 --> 01:20:25,518
若他们要我们知难而退
If they were sending us a message

777
01:20:25,620 --> 01:20:28,612
那该会说这是他们做的
they'd want us to know it was them

778
01:20:28,824 --> 01:20:32,692
除了他们想故弄玄虚，声东击西
Except they could inspire
the confusion we're going through now

779
01:20:32,894 --> 01:20:34,987
总统先生，准备好通讯了
Mr President, we're uplinked

780
01:20:38,366 --> 01:20:44,498
尼总统，美国发生严重核爆事件
President Nemerov, there's been a
major nuclear event in the United States

781
01:20:44,739 --> 01:20:46,206
死伤惨重
Loss of life is severe

782
01:20:46,441 --> 01:20:49,035
这绝不是意外    这绝不是意外
- It was no accident.
- It was not an accident

783
01:20:49,244 --> 01:20:52,645
我们还不知道核弹从哪儿来... 
We don't yet know where
it came from, we don't... 

784
01:20:52,848 --> 01:20:58,514
我们还没确定核弹的来源... 
We have not yet ascertained the
source of this weapon. Rest assured... 

785
01:20:58,720 --> 01:21:03,453
我们还没确定核弹的来源
We have not yet ascertained
the source of this weapon

786
01:21:04,059 --> 01:21:08,758
但可保证我国定将严惩真凶
But rest assured those responsible
will be deALt with most severely

787
01:21:10,765 --> 01:21:13,256
他在试探我们
He's fishing

788
01:21:13,468 --> 01:21:15,436
给他回覆
Send our reply

789
01:21:17,439 --> 01:21:19,464
这么快有回应
Whoa, that was a little fast

790
01:21:19,674 --> 01:21:22,802
请接受俄国人民最深切的慰问
"Please accept the deepest
sympathies of the Russian people."

791
01:21:23,011 --> 01:21:26,310
若是蓄意施袭，诚是空前的暴行
"If it was deliberate,
this is a crime without precedent."

792
01:21:26,514 --> 01:21:29,540
是哪个疯子所为？目的何在？
"What madman would do such a thing
and for what purpose?"

793
01:21:29,784 --> 01:21:33,083
敬请相信俄国与此暴行绝无关连
"You must believe that Russia had
nothing to do with this infamous act."

794
01:21:33,288 --> 01:21:36,746
是预谋，他早有此着
It's canned.
He prepared that in advance

795
01:21:37,826 --> 01:21:42,263
尼总统，如今我们无理由怀疑
President Nemerov, we've no reason
to suspect Russian involvement... 

796
01:21:42,464 --> 01:21:43,931
俄国与此事有关
... at this time... 

797
01:21:44,332 --> 01:21:49,861
但我们会竭力自卫，免再受袭击
... but we will protect ourselves
from further aggression

798
01:21:51,172 --> 01:21:53,504
他认为是我们做的
He thinks we did this

799
01:21:53,675 --> 01:21:56,940
我们必须显示军力
We must demonstrate
the strength of our weapons

800
01:21:57,145 --> 01:22:02,742
让他们明白攻打俄国就是找死
They have to understand that
attacking Russia would be suicide

801
01:22:02,984 --> 01:22:06,545
加强戒备
Increase the alert status

802
01:22:42,857 --> 01:22:46,987
接收到间断的讯号，方位020
TAO, EW. I'm picking up
intermittent radar, bearing 020

803
01:22:48,730 --> 01:22:50,129
哪儿？
Where?

804
01:22:52,901 --> 01:22:54,300
没有了
Now it's gone

805
01:23:02,477 --> 01:23:04,468
这儿，但讯号微弱
There. It's a weak signAL

806
01:23:04,679 --> 01:23:06,670
有敌机来袭
TAO, inbound contact

807
01:23:12,487 --> 01:23:14,011
相同方位有多架敌机
Multiples on the same bearing

808
01:23:16,191 --> 01:23:18,386
注意！    敌机迅速来袭
- Vampire, vampire!
- Fast movers inbound

809
01:23:18,593 --> 01:23:20,993
有七、八、九架敌机！
I got seven, eight, nine of them!

810
01:23:46,621 --> 01:23:49,351
导弹是从俄军战机发射的
The missiles definitely came
from Russian aircraft

811
01:23:49,557 --> 01:23:52,924
母舰还保得住，但不能执行任务
Grennel thinks he can save the ship,
but flight ops are out

812
01:23:55,597 --> 01:23:58,498
我没下令攻打母舰
I ordered no such attack

813
01:23:58,666 --> 01:24:01,328
请保持冷静，先让我们调查清楚
You must not respond to this action
until we investigate all possibilities

814
01:24:01,569 --> 01:24:03,799
先让我们调查清楚
"... until we investigate all possibilities."

815
01:24:04,005 --> 01:24:06,030
正如车臣事件？
Like you did in Chechnya?

816
01:24:06,241 --> 01:24:09,540
尼总统，谁在控制你的军队？
Mr President, who is in control
of your armed forces?

817
01:24:12,013 --> 01:24:15,039
是你们在广岛投掷原子弹
You dropped the bomb on Hiroshima

818
01:24:15,250 --> 01:24:18,219
是你们在长崎投掷原子弹
You dropped the bomb on Nagasaki

819
01:24:18,553 --> 01:24:21,215
别拿车臣事件来教训我
Do not lecture me on Chechnya

820
01:24:21,456 --> 01:24:25,187
拿车臣事件来教训我
"... lecture me on Chechnya."

821
01:24:25,393 --> 01:24:32,265
事实上现在我们已跟俄国开战
Mr President, we are now at a
de facto state of war with the Russians

822
01:24:37,839 --> 01:24:42,799
昨天勒约翰在海法，定要找到他
John Clark was in Haifa yesterday.
We have to find him right away

823
01:24:43,011 --> 01:24:44,876
看看钆的含量读数
Wow.
Look at that gadolinium reading

824
01:24:45,080 --> 01:24:47,640
质量数很高
Yeah. The mass fraction is huge

825
01:24:47,849 --> 01:24:50,750
快联络迪伦，我会等
OK, connect me to Dillon. I'll hold

826
01:24:51,953 --> 01:24:55,389
就在这儿，萨凡纳河
There it is. Savannah River

827
01:24:56,324 --> 01:24:58,815
没错    什么没错？
- Oh, yeah.
- Oh, yeah, what?

828
01:24:59,060 --> 01:25:00,687
那边有钆的问题
They had a gadolinium problem

829
01:25:00,895 --> 01:25:04,695
汉福的做法不对，产生太多i
Hanford does it another way,
and generate too much promethium

830
01:25:04,899 --> 01:25:07,390
慢着，你可否解释清楚一点？
Hold on. Can you translate that
into English?

831
01:25:09,270 --> 01:25:13,673
68年2月铀来自河上这间工厂
This plutonium came from the DOE
plant at Savannah River, February '68

832
01:25:13,875 --> 01:25:17,333
源自K反应堆，还知道是哪部分
from K reactor. We even know
which part of K reactor

833
01:25:17,545 --> 01:25:22,073
这是我们造的铀？    美国产品
- Wait. This is our plutonium?
- Made in the USA

834
01:25:24,219 --> 01:25:26,619
迪伦，我一定要找到老卡
Dillon, you've got to find Cabot

835
01:25:33,628 --> 01:25:36,358
你想说服我们发动第一击？
Are you advocating we launch
a first strike?

836
01:25:36,564 --> 01:25:41,524
不是！已经有第一击，事已至此
It is not a first strike! There's ALready
been a first strike, and a second

837
01:25:41,736 --> 01:25:44,034
你还不明白    我不明白
- Don't you get it?
- No, I don't get it!

838
01:25:44,239 --> 01:25:47,902
为何要用核弹？这不合理
I don't understand why we have
to nuke them! It's not reasonable

839
01:25:48,109 --> 01:25:50,202
悉尼，混帐！
Sidney, goddamn it!

840
01:25:50,411 --> 01:25:53,141
他们打沉我们的航空母舰！
They practically sank
an aircraft carrier!

841
