1021
01:45:32,292 --> 01:45:35,386
我只是想传达情报
I just need to send some information

1022
01:45:36,963 --> 01:45:39,488
总统为什么要听你说？
What makes you think
the President will listen to you?

1023
01:45:43,470 --> 01:45:45,461
他没此必要
He doesn't have to

1024
01:45:45,839 --> 01:45:48,000
轰炸机有多接近？
How close are the bombers?

1025
01:45:48,942 --> 01:45:55,006
它们进出波兰上空
They're slipping in and out of radar
over Poland

1026
01:45:59,119 --> 01:46:03,783
出动导弹兵团
Activate the missile regiments

1027
01:46:11,064 --> 01:46:14,727
系统在你下令后一分钟才启动
The launch sequence takes a minute
to process after you give the order

1028
01:46:14,935 --> 01:46:19,065
下令前，要先核对身分
Before the order can be taken,
an ID check must be performed

1029
01:46:24,177 --> 01:46:27,806
我的号码是... 
Mine is the...  My number is... 

1030
01:46:28,949 --> 01:46:31,816
数下来... 第三个号码
... the third one... third number down
from the top

1031
01:46:32,586 --> 01:46:34,713
你的命令是什么？
Your orders, sir?

1032
01:46:34,955 --> 01:46:37,423
出击    抱歉，总统？
- Strike.
- I'm sorry, sir?

1033
01:46:37,624 --> 01:46:40,024
我下令出击
I give the order to strike

1034
01:46:40,227 --> 01:46:44,596
要马上作两人授命，下令出击
Under the two-man rule, the order
to strike must now be confirmed

1035
01:46:46,500 --> 01:46:48,968
罗拔，看在老天份上
Bob, for the love of God

1036
01:46:49,169 --> 01:46:50,966
动手好了
Just do it

1037
01:46:56,009 --> 01:47:00,139
国务卿奥悉尼，第四个号码
Sidney Owens, Secretary of State.
It's the fourth number down

1038
01:47:09,656 --> 01:47:12,989
已作了两人授命，下令出击
The order to strike has now been
confirmed by the two-man rule

1039
01:47:13,193 --> 01:47:17,459
出击的命令已确定，启动系统
NMCC, strike order has been
confirmed. Start the sequence

1040
01:47:17,664 --> 01:47:20,394
热线有动静    早已给他们机会
- We've got activity on the hotline.
- They've had their chance

1041
01:47:20,600 --> 01:47:21,862
不，有人在跟老尼通话
No, somebody's tALking to the Kremlin

1042
01:47:28,575 --> 01:47:32,306
说“美国是恐怖袭击的受害者”
It says, "America has been the victim
of a terrorist attack."

1043
01:47:32,579 --> 01:47:37,039
你应该想像得到我方有不少揣测
As you can imagine, there has
been much confusion here... 

1044
01:47:37,684 --> 01:47:39,447
人心惶惶
... and fear

1045
01:47:39,686 --> 01:47:42,712
但我们知道不是俄国动武
But we know the weapon
was not Russian

1046
01:47:42,956 --> 01:47:46,357
“但我们知道不是俄国动武”
"But we know the weapon
was not Russian."

1047
01:47:46,560 --> 01:47:48,118
怎么回事？
What the hell is going on?

1048
01:47:55,535 --> 01:47:58,299
照我说的打
Type exactly what I say

1049
01:47:58,472 --> 01:48:01,100
你究竟是谁？
Who are we tALking to?

1050
01:48:03,743 --> 01:48:07,736
积克，我跟局长在莫斯科见过你
Ryan. I met you in Moscow with
Bill Cabot. 

1051
01:48:07,881 --> 01:48:09,405
今天他在巴尔的摩死了
He died today in BALtimore

1052
01:48:09,616 --> 01:48:12,676
中止通讯    已启动核武系统
- Cut him off.
- Launch sequence has begun

1053
01:48:12,919 --> 01:48:14,386
两个月前
Two months ago

1054
01:48:14,654 --> 01:48:18,249
新法西斯主义者斯拿买了原子弹
a neo-fascist named Dressler bought
an A-bomb on the black market

1055
01:48:18,492 --> 01:48:22,155
中止通讯    无法中止系统操作
- Cut him off.
- The system can't be cut off

1056
01:48:22,362 --> 01:48:24,387
那快找人阻止他
Then get someone to stop him

1057
01:48:24,598 --> 01:48:26,759
他雇用三个俄罗斯... 
- He paid three disaffected Russian... 

1058
01:48:26,900 --> 01:48:28,868
科学家修复原子弹
- "scientists to make the bomb active."

1059
01:48:29,069 --> 01:48:31,970
然后把它送来美国，一个姓马的
"He shipped it to the US,
where a man named Mason"

1060
01:48:32,172 --> 01:48:36,768
是他搞鬼，令我们两国起纷争
was hired to deliver the bomb and
set our countries on a collision course

1061
01:48:37,143 --> 01:48:41,307
胡说八道，他是中情局
This is madness. He is CIA

1062
01:48:41,515 --> 01:48:44,746
我们绝不能听信他们的间谍
We cannot hang our fate
on the word of their spy

1063
01:48:44,985 --> 01:48:48,921
听多一点没害处吧？
What is the harm of listening
a bit more?

1064
01:48:53,026 --> 01:48:55,688
你想我怎么做？
What are you asking of me?

1065
01:49:04,738 --> 01:49:05,966
就此罢手
Back down

1066
01:49:10,410 --> 01:49:14,107
有什么可保证霍总统也会收手？
What guarantee do I have that
President Fowler will follow suit?

1067
01:49:15,448 --> 01:49:17,006
没有保证
None

1068
01:49:20,053 --> 01:49:23,386
看见吗？他在浪费时间
You see? He is wasting time

1069
01:49:23,590 --> 01:49:25,820
我们得出击，时间无多
We must launch now.
We have only moments

1070
01:49:28,261 --> 01:49:32,459
我知道你跟巴尔的摩的核爆无关
Sir, I know you had nothing to do
with the BALtimore bomb

1071
01:49:32,666 --> 01:49:37,126
你也知道，但你还是要攻打我们
and you know you didn't, but you're
still about to launch a nuclear strike

1072
01:49:37,337 --> 01:49:40,670
说够了    这都是恐惧之故
- Yes, sir. That's all, Dr Ryan.
- This is about fear

1073
01:49:40,874 --> 01:49:43,104
害怕你们的导弹，我们的潜艇
Fear of your missiles,
fear of our subs

1074
01:49:43,310 --> 01:49:45,278
害怕做弱者，害怕犯错
Fear of being weak,
of making a mistake

1075
01:49:45,478 --> 01:49:49,642
害怕对方率先制造这些烂核弹！
the fear of the other guy that had us
build these bombs in the first place!

1076
01:49:53,119 --> 01:49:54,381
没通讯了
It stopped

1077
01:49:57,524 --> 01:49:58,821
他们中止了他的通讯
They cut him off

1078
01:49:59,826 --> 01:50:01,259
他们会出击
They are going to strike

1079
01:50:01,461 --> 01:50:04,555
准备启动核武系统
Prepare the launch orders now

1080
01:50:19,245 --> 01:50:21,042
30秒后发射
30 seconds to launch

1081
01:50:21,214 --> 01:50:23,375
老天... 总统先生？
Oh, my God. Mr President?

1082
01:50:29,856 --> 01:50:31,153
我下令... 

1083
01:50:31,358 --> 01:50:33,053
俄国战略部队撤消战备状态

1084
01:50:33,259 --> 01:50:36,490
暂时我们会保持在防卫戒备状态
We will maintain our defensive alert
for the moment

1085
01:50:36,696 --> 01:50:39,460
但是已撤退攻击部队
but our offensive forces
are withdrawn

1086
01:50:39,666 --> 01:50:40,792
“若你照这样做”
"If you match this, 

1087
01:50:40,900 --> 01:50:44,336
“我建议双方撤消备战状态”
I propose a phased
mutuAL stand down over five hours."

1088
01:50:46,439 --> 01:50:48,464
关闭核武系统
Stop the launch sequence

1089
01:50:48,675 --> 01:50:52,406
这是莱上将，马上关闭核武系统
Lasseter here. Flash override.
Stop the sequence!

1090
01:50:53,480 --> 01:50:57,109
撤走战机，进入三级紧急状态
Order the planes to stand down.
Take us to DEFCON-3

1091
01:50:57,317 --> 01:51:01,219
找人问积克我可以用电话了吗？
And would somebody ask Mr Ryan
if I can use the phone now?

1092
01:51:31,084 --> 01:51:33,075
你还在这儿
You're still here

1093
01:52:22,368 --> 01:52:24,734
美国

1094
01:53:44,083 --> 01:53:46,381
俄罗斯

1095
01:54:45,044 --> 01:54:49,447
没有什么比我们今周所做的
There is no more fitting memoriAL
for those who perished in this tragedy

1096
01:54:49,649 --> 01:54:51,844
更能悼念这次惨剧的受害者
than the steps we've taken this week

1097
01:54:52,085 --> 01:54:54,076
以求多国通力合作
toward a multinational campaign

1098
01:54:54,320 --> 01:54:58,347
大规模销毁破坏力强大的军备
to root out and eliminate
weapons of mass destruction

1099
01:54:59,692 --> 01:55:01,557
我们有此目标
We embarked on this course

1100
01:55:01,661 --> 01:55:05,028
全因吸取了重大的教训
 because
we have learned, at too great a cost

1101
01:55:05,231 --> 01:55:08,598
明白到若我们动用最强大的武器
that if the most powerful weapons
ever created are unleashed

1102
01:55:08,801 --> 01:55:12,737
那不是因为愤恨，而是恐惧之故
they will be fired not in anger,
but in fear

1103
01:55:12,939 --> 01:55:14,270
雷博士
Dr Ryan

1104
01:55:15,642 --> 01:55:17,473
古先生
Mr Grushkov

1105
01:55:17,844 --> 01:55:21,507
今天... 是个大好日子
It is... a lovely day

1106
01:55:23,383 --> 01:55:24,873
对
Yeah

1107
01:55:25,718 --> 01:55:30,178
抱歉，这是...     梅医生，幸会
- I'm sorry, this is... 
- Dr Muller. How do you do?

1108
01:55:31,291 --> 01:55:33,555
幸会
Nice to meet you

1109
01:55:35,194 --> 01:55:37,594
为何我不为此感到意外？
Why am I not surprised
you know her name?

1110
01:55:39,866 --> 01:55:43,097
我们的朋友比利以为我是个间谍
Our friend William thought
I was a spy

1111
01:55:43,303 --> 01:55:45,931
当然他无法证实这个
Of course, he could never prove it

1112
01:55:48,207 --> 01:55:49,970
他从未说过你们是朋友
He never told me you were friends

1113
01:55:51,110 --> 01:55:53,578
也许他跟你不太熟络
Maybe he didn't know you well enough

1114
01:55:56,249 --> 01:55:58,979
他说他有个俄罗斯线人
He told me he had a source in Russia

1115
01:56:01,254 --> 01:56:03,279
“打开秘密渠道”？
"To keep the back channels open?"

1116
01:56:05,224 --> 01:56:07,283
“以免灾难发生”
"In hopes of staving off disaster."

1117
01:56:07,527 --> 01:56:11,827
甘尼迪说过我们最大的共通之处
Kennedy said,
"Our most basic common link"

1118
01:56:12,031 --> 01:56:15,762
就是同居住于这地球上
"is that we all inhabit
this small planet. "

1119
01:56:17,370 --> 01:56:19,998
呼吸相同的空气
"We all breathe the same air. "

1120
01:56:20,640 --> 01:56:25,134
大家都重视儿女的将来
"We all cherish our children's future...  "

1121
01:56:25,645 --> 01:56:28,307
还有我们生有尽时
"... and we're all mortal. "

1122
01:56:29,182 --> 01:56:34,347
我会好怀念... 跟比利合作的日子
I will miss... so very much
tALking to William

1123
01:56:36,322 --> 01:56:37,789
我也是
Me too

1124
01:56:38,725 --> 01:56:42,183
也许日后有机会
Perhaps from time to time

1125
01:56:42,428 --> 01:56:45,056
我们可以合作
you and I can tALk

1126
01:56:45,264 --> 01:56:47,596
乐意之至
Yeah, I'd like that

1127
01:56:50,336 --> 01:56:51,633
这是什么？
What is this?

1128
01:56:52,805 --> 01:56:56,673
庆祝你们订婚的小礼物
A modest gift for your engagement

1129
01:56:58,945 --> 01:57:00,674
他... 今早才向我求婚
He... he just asked me this morning

1130
01:57:00,880 --> 01:57:03,576
我们还没告诉任何人
We haven't told anybody about it

1131
01:57:04,851 --> 01:57:07,513
你怎么可能知道？
How... how could you possibly know?
